      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "The following primers were used  : spacer region-specific primers, spacer region 33 specific (5′ACACCGACATGACGGCGG3′) and spacer region 34 specific (5′CGACGGTGTGGGCGAGG3′); IS6110 (5′GGACAACGCCGAATTGCG′3 and 5′TAGGCGTCGGTGACAAAGGCCAC′3), and Mycobacterium genus-specific TB11 (sequence 5′ACCAACGATGGTGTGTCCAT3′) and TB12 (sequence 5′CTTGTCGAACCGCATACCCT3′)."
